        "name": "Sticky Fire",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You send a bubble of viscous liquid that sparks into flame. Make a spell attack roll against the target\u2019s AC, dealing 1d8 fire damage and 1d8 persistent fire damage on a hit. The target is enfeebled 1 until they recover from their persistent fire damage.",
